      "text": "Gomiers un wiﬁ wi\nKarra-Wihri/ tas Nams\nTogarmas/ kas pee teem S\nneem prett Seemeli/ ar wiﬁ\nwinna Karrogeem/ dauds L\nschu ar tewin.\n"
