      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ap to Gaddo Ga\nnabksi tu us to Semmi/ kas\nta Sobbinx irr atkat atw\nun fapulzeta no dauds Lau\nus Israëta Kalneem/ kas\nMittefchanns irr tspohstiit t\npuschi/ kad ta patti Semme\nwesta buhs no teem Laudim/\ntee wiﬀnotut drohschi dshwa\n"
